plicants will receive $1,000. Seven scholarships were available to eligible UIC undergraduate students. The awarding of scholarships is based on a combination of academic merit and financial need. Students in all fields are eligible.   Congratulations to Our Current Awardees:  Scholarship Awardees  2016-2017  Michael Cheong  Kevin Chung  Vivian Jin  Jack Leick  Queena Luu  Katharine Xie             © Copyright 2014-2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois      Footer Navigation   University of Illinois Hospital & Health Sciences System Fulbright Google Translate Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Privacy Policy  Contact Us           Cookie Settings   